    {
      "id": "sybil_8_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_8",
      "description": "Offering a mechanically robust E92 M3 featuring the high-revving S65 4.0L V8 engine. This unit maintains exceptional valvetrain integrity and has undergone preventative rod bearing replacement to ensure long-term reliability of the crank journals. The 6-speed manual transmission provides tactile engagement, sending power through the M Variable Differential Lock for precise corner-exit traction. The chassis is equipped with Electronic Damper Control (EDC), offering adjustable compression and rebound settings to suit varied driving dynamics. While the exterior shows minor road-going patina, the powertrain remains in peak operating condition with linear power delivery up to the 8,400 RPM redline and a rigid, carbon-fiber-reinforced plastic (CFRP) roof for a lower center of gravity.",
