      "description": "This vehicle strikes the perfect balance between a well-loved driver and a meticulously maintained classic. The exterior retains a deep, lustrous finish, though minor stone chips on the front fascia tell the story of enjoyable highway miles. Inside, the cabin remains a sanctuary; the premium leather seats show only light natural creasing, and every toggle and switch functions with tactile precision. Under the hood, the engine hums with consistent strength, backed by a comprehensive service record that ensures peace of mind. It handles with the poise you\u2019d expect from a car that has been sheltered in a garage and treated with respect. While not a museum piece, it is an exceptionally clean, dependable example that turns heads at every stoplight. Ready for immediate enjoyment without the need for additional work.",
